						<p>Incomplete. Records that Āyam Aḍaikkalaṅgkāttār and Eṟappar and others (endowed some gift) inorder to burn a twilight lamp, for the merit of Śrīmadunāyakkar Kṛishṇappa Nāyakkaraiyyaṉ and Vēlūr Eṟa Bomma Nāyakkar, at the temple in Dēvikkāpuram.</p>						

